The formulation that excludes your participation is, they will sign the contract, the other party will sign the contract. This goal does not depend on you. The goal when you ensure the signing of your actions, your efforts, this goal, which depends on you, and it will stimulate you more, motivate you more to achieve it during the negotiations.

